name: Web Primitives / Enabled or Disabled 0.0
description:
Enabled or Disabled 0.0 from Web Primitives collection. A series of interactive internet art in form made by and based on web technologies.

This work is purely made by html as part of #purehtmlart challenge.
 
In this collection, I try to experiment with the most primitive and fundamental elements of web pages(HTML elements) as well as the possibilities that browsers give us in our daily life.
